  "subject": "Fix: Move CCSDK/SDNC release jobs to C7",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Move CCSDK/SDNC release jobs to C7\n\nThere is an issue detected in C8 at the time of signing the\nrelease tag which is still under investigation.\n\nUse C7 for now, this will not affect the artifacts since these\nwere built in the stage job with C8. This job exclusively releases\nthe artifacts without rebuilding them.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: Jessica Wagantall <jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org>\nChange-Id: Id2eab9da35fb44f1889bf4a10ef2acf3c1f919e6\n",
